nodes.text: Dark Times—Out of the Wilderness 2 is the nineteenth issue of the Star Wars: Dark Times comic series and the second in the Out of the Wilderness story arc.

Everyone is after fugitive Jedi Dass Jennir. An assassin broke into an Imperial facility seeking information about Jennir's whereabouts, and the specifics of what was stolen have put Darth Vader on Jennir's trail—with the Emperor's blessing! Even the outlaw crew of the Uhumele are searching for their erstwhile companion.
